    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature targets you with an attack.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are aware of the attack and are not @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard} to the triggering attack. </p><hr /><p>You quickly Change Shape into a smaller size to avoid getting hit. You gain a circumstance bonus to AC, Fortitude DC, and Reflex DC against the triggering attack equal to the number of steps between your sizes when you Change Shape (+1 if you are one size smaller, +2 if you are two sizes smaller, and so on).</p>",
